Class ContactMethodElement

java.lang.Object

org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.metadataelements.ContactMethodElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
MetadataElement
public class ContactMethodElement extends AttributedMetadataElement
ContactMethodElement contains the properties and header for a contract method retrieved from the metadata repository.
